content:
Set Up Omni-Channel to route incoming work items from different service channels to qualified, available agents in your contact center.

Omni Supervisor is available in: Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

We recommend using Enhanced Omni-Channel. Enhanced Omni-Channel features better experiences for agents and supervisors than Standard Omni-Channel.

To set up Omni-Channel:

In the Quick Find box under Setup, enter Omni-Channel Home, and then select Omni-Channel Home.
Click a link to perform a setup task or click Learn More for more information about a task.
Check out service channel instances created for your company.
Hover over icons for warnings if they appear.

Create Custom Report Types for Omni-Channel

Migrate from Legacy Live Agent to Omni-Channel for Chat
title: Setting Up and Configuring Omni-Channel in Salesforce
